(30, 1, 'HOT-COLD / BOD INCUBATOR / REFRIGERATED CABINET', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">Superb low temperature incubation performance using a noiseless HBP compressor cooling system which reduces water evaporation within the chambers.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">Operating Features</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&Oslash;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">Temperature control: 0&deg;C to 60&deg;C</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&Oslash;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">Microprocessor PID control</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&Oslash;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">Simple calibration and auto-tuning functions<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&Oslash;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">Digital timer with Delayed ON/OFF function: 99 days to 99 hr. 59 min<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&Oslash;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">High temperature limit setting and open-</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&Oslash;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">door alarm</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&Oslash;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">Convenient preset function for 3 most commonly used temperature settings<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&Oslash;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">Up to 9 temperature steps and maximum 200 cycles of repetition programmable for each profile<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&Oslash;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif;\">Adjustable three-step fan speed with defrosting time and period control</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Wingdings; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-fo